A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of data streams flowing through neon-lit fiber optic cables in a dark urban environment, with glowing cyan and magenta packets of information traveling in segmented chunks through transparent tubes, breaking apart and reassembling as they move. The scene shows a massive server tower in the background with pulsing lights, while in the foreground, streams of luminescent data fragments cascade like a digital waterfall, each chunk distinctly separated yet flowing continuously. Rain falls through holographic grid patterns in the sky, reflecting the electric glow of the data streams below. The atmosphere is moody and technological, emphasizing the concept of continuous flow and processing of information in motion.
